5pt;\\"> <\\/span>You may advise other consumers on what to do to get the most from a creator. Two perfect<span style=\\"letter-spacing: 0.05pt;\\"> <\\/span>examples<span style=\\"letter-spacing: -1.1pt;\\"> <\\/span>are:<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n    <p class=\\"MsoListParagraph\\" style=''margin: 8.45pt 6.5pt 0.0001pt 41.05pt; text-indent: -18.05pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: \\"Times New Roman\\"; text-align: justify; line-height: 29.7733px;''><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 32.48px; font-family: Arial;\\">&bull;<span style=''font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \\"Times New Roman\\";''>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\\/span><\\/span><b><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 32.48px;\\">For Subscribers<\\/span><\\/b><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 32.48px;\\">: <i>&ldquo;if you can&rsquo;t relate to military terms, you may not enjoy this content<span style=\\"letter-spacing: 0.05pt;\\"> <\\/span>creator.&rdquo;<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/i><\\/span><\\/p>\\n    <p class=\\"MsoListParagraph\\" style=''margin: 0.1pt 5.7pt 0.0001pt 41.05pt; text-indent: -18.05pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: \\"Times New Roman\\"; text-align: justify; line-height: 29.3333px;''><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 32px; font-family: Arial;\\">&bull;<span style=''font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \\"Times New Roman\\";''>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <\\/span><\\/span><b><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 32px;\\">For creators<\\/span><\\/b><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 32px;\\">: <i>I think offering a better video quality will help connect with your audience<span style=\\"letter-spacing: 0.05pt;\\"> <\\/span>bett