<span lang=\\"EN-US\\">To use your account and start leaving reviews, you must update your info. To do this, simply<span style=\\"letter-spacing: 0.05pt;\\"> <\\/span>provide your full name, date of birth, country, and password. You also have to choose an account<span style=\\"letter-spacing: -2.85pt;\\"> <\\/span>type,<span style=\\"letter-spacing: -0.55pt;\\"> <\\/span>whether<span style=\\"letter-spacing: 0.25pt;\\"> <\\/span>creator<span style=\\"letter-spacing: -1pt;\\"> <\\/span>or<span style=\\"letter-spacing: 0.2pt;\\"> <\\/span>reviewer.<span style=\\"letter-spacing: -0.5pt;\\"> <\\/span>To<span style=\\"letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\\"> <\\/span>write<span style=\\"letter-spacing: -0.5pt;\\"> <\\/span>reviews,<span style=\\"letter-spacing: -0.55pt;\\"> <\\/span>you<span style=\\"letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\\"> <\\/span>should<span style=\\"letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\\"> <\\/span>choose<span style=\\"letter-spacing: -0.5pt;\\"> <\\/span>&ldquo;reviewer.&rdquo;<o:p><\\/o:p><\\/span><\\/p>\\n    <h2 style=''margin: 7.85pt 0cm 0.0001pt 5.05pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \\"Times New Roman\\";''><span lang=\\"EN-US\\" style=\\"color: rgb(31, 55, 98);\\">How<span style=\\"letter-spacing: -0.25pt;\\"> <\\/span>To<span style=\\"letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\\"> <\\/span>Write<span style=\\"letter-spacing: -0.55pt;\\"> <\\/span>Reviews<span style=\\"letter-spacing: 0.2pt;\\"> <\\/span>on<span style=\\"letter-spacing: -0.05pt;\\"> <\\/span>The<span style=\\"letter-spacing: 0.9pt;\\"> <\\/span>Privy<span style=\\"letter-spacing: -0.55pt;\\"> <\\/span>Website<\\/span><span lang=\\"EN-US\\">\\n            <o:p><\\/o:p>\\n        <\\/span><\\/h2>\\n    <p class=\\"MsoBodyText\\" style=''margin: 0.05pt 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \\"Times New Roman\\";''><b><span lang=\\"EN-US\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/b><\\/p>\\n    <p class=\\"MsoNormal\\" style=''margin: 0cm 5.4pt 0.0001pt 5.05pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: \\"Times New Roman\\"; text